<!-- SS FAQ — rebuilt from star-story-theme/sections/ws-faw.liquid -->
<!-- Settings hardcoded from product.json ws_faw_imfAgq -->
<!-- FAQ toggle icons from original Star Story Shopify CDN -->

<div class="rb-faq-shopify-section" id="faq">
  <h1 style="text-align: center; padding: 20px 20px 0px 20px;">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <div class="rb-faq-container">

    <div class="rb-faq-container-item">
      <input style="display:none!important;" type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-tab1" class="tab-toggle">
      <label for="ss-faq-tab1" class="rb-faq-question">What is a natal chart?</label>
      <div class="rb-faq-answer"><p>A natal chart, also known as a birth chart, is a map of the sky at the exact moment and location of your birth. It shows the positions of the planets and other celestial bodies in relation to the Earth and provides insights into your personality, strengths, challenges, and potential life path.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="rb-faq-container-item">
      <input style="display:none!important;" type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-tab2" class="tab-toggle">
      <label for="ss-faq-tab2" class="rb-faq-question">How is this book customized?</label>
      <div class="rb-faq-answer"><p>Each book is customized based on the specific date, time, and place of your birth. This allows us to create a unique natal chart and personalized interpretations that are specific to you.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="rb-faq-container-item">
      <input style="display:none!important;" type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-tab3" class="tab-toggle">
      <label for="ss-faq-tab3" class="rb-faq-question">Can I order a book as a gift for someone else?</label>
      <div class="rb-faq-answer"><p>Yes, you can! Just provide the birth details of the person you are gifting the book to. You can also add a personal message to be included in the book.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="rb-faq-container-item">
      <input style="display:none!important;" type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-tab4" class="tab-toggle">
      <label for="ss-faq-tab4" class="rb-faq-question">What if I don't know my exact birth time?</label>
      <div class="rb-faq-answer"><p>While the exact birth time provides the most accurate chart, we can still create a chart using an estimated time or a general time (like morning, afternoon, evening). However, for the most precise reading, we recommend trying to obtain the exact birth time from a birth certificate or family records.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="rb-faq-container-item">
      <input style="display:none!important;" type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-tab5" class="tab-toggle">
      <label for="ss-faq-tab5" class="rb-faq-question">How accurate does the birth location need to be?</label>
      <div class="rb-faq-answer"><p>The more precise the location, the better the chart will reflect your astrological profile. Providing the city or town is usually sufficient.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="rb-faq-container-item">
      <input style="display:none!important;" type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-tab6" class="tab-toggle">
      <label for="ss-faq-tab6" class="rb-faq-question">What does the book include?</label>
      <div class="rb-faq-answer"><p>The book includes a detailed natal chart, interpretations of your sun, moon, and rising signs, analysis of the planetary aspects, and personalized insights into various life areas such as career, relationships, and personal growth.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="rb-faq-container-item">
      <input style="display:none!important;" type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-tab7" class="tab-toggle">
      <label for="ss-faq-tab7" class="rb-faq-question">What size is the book and how many pages does it have?</label>
      <div class="rb-faq-answer"><p>The book is 8 x 8" (20 x 20cm), and the number of pages is 90.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="rb-faq-container-item">
      <input style="display:none!important;" type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-tab8" class="tab-toggle">
      <label for="ss-faq-tab8" class="rb-faq-question">How long will it take to receive my book?</label>
      <div class="rb-faq-answer"><p>The book is fully customised by our astrologists, so it takes 7 days to create. Printing and shipping can add another 7 days. Typically, you can expect to receive your book within 14 days of ordering.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="rb-faq-container-item">
      <input style="display:none!important;" type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-tab9" class="tab-toggle">
      <label for="ss-faq-tab9" class="rb-faq-question">Can I make changes to my order after it's been placed?</label>
      <div class="rb-faq-answer"><p>We begin processing orders within 24 hours after you fill in the form after purchase, so changes may not always be possible. Please contact our customer service team as soon as possible if you need to make adjustments.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="rb-faq-container-item">
      <input style="display:none!important;" type="checkbox" id="ss-faq-tab10" class="tab-toggle">
      <label for="ss-faq-tab10" class="rb-faq-question">What is your return policy?</label>
      <div class="rb-faq-answer"><p>Since each book is custom-made, we generally do not accept returns. However, if there is an error in the information or a defect in the book, please contact us, and we will make it right.</p></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
.rb-faq-shopify-section {
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    padding-bottom: 61px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    background: #e4dcca;
}
.rb-faq-container {
    margin: auto;
    max-width: 1240px;
}
.rb-faq-container-item {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #00000021;
}
.rb-faq-question::after {
    color: #ffffff;
    content: url("https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0883/5606/1457/files/Icon_wrap_2.svg?v=1721072920");
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
}
.rb-faq-question {
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex !important;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0);
    padding: 8px 20px;
    font-weight: bold;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #1a3050;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    letter-spacing: normal;
}
.rb-faq-answer p {
    margin: 0;
}
.rb-faq-question:hover {
    color: #1a3050;
}
.rb-faq-answer {
    padding: 0px 20px;
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    visibility: hidden;
    will-change: height;
    transform: translateY(25px);
    transition: all .2s ease;
    -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
}
.tab-toggle:checked ~ .rb-faq-answer {
    transform: translateY(0);
    padding: 15px 20px;
    height: auto;
    padding-top: 0px;
    opacity: 1;
    overflow: unset;
    visibility: visible;
    transition: all .3s ease, opacity 1s ease, height .3s ease;
    color: #1a3050;
    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0);
}
.tab-toggle:checked ~ .rb-faq-question::after {
    content: url("https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0883/5606/1457/files/Icon_wrap_1.svg?v=1721072920");
}
.tab-toggle {
    display: none;
}
</style>

